trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of change occurring in a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o tipo de alteração ocorrer numa coleção de <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListsChangedType enumeration indicates that an element has been added or removed from a managed collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: A enumeração de DesignerActionListsChangedType indica que um elemento foi adicionado ou removido da coleção gerida de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objetos.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class, which is associated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Esta enumeração é utilizada no <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>classe que está associado a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>eventos.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects, it does not directly raise events.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Apesar do <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>classe é uma coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objetos, não gere diretamente eventos.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objetos foram adicionados à coleção.

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objetos foram removidos da coleção.
